#, fuzzy
msgid "Exporter protocol. OLTP is the OpenTelemetry protocol."
msgstr "导出协议。OLTP 是 OpenTelemetry 协议。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/infinispan-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
