msgstr "将在追踪收集器（此处为 Jaeger）中注册的服务名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/infinispan-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enables 'security' category tracing."
msgstr "启用“安全”类别的追踪功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/infinispan-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See below the equivalent in XML and JSON."
msgstr "请参见下方的 XML 和 JSON 对应格式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/infinispan-dev-services.adoc
